text: Christian German School Chiang Mai (, CDSC; ) is a German international school in Chiang Mai, Thailand. It serves from nursery to secondary stage II."Secondary School." Christian German School Chiang Mai. Retrieved on 5 September 2018. The current nursery building opened in June 2013."Our School." Christian German School Chiang Mai.
